title: Crumbed Haloumi & Chicken Burger  with Kumara Wedges & Creamy Slaw
description: Sometimes a burger is the only thing that will satisfy! Try this new twist on a classic, with golden-crumbed haloumi and chicken drizzled in a BBQ-cherry sauce that’s the perfect combination of fruity and tangy.
